  <brief_title>Fexofenadine Study On Filipino Children for The Relief of Perennial And Intermittent Allergic Rhinitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Monitored Release Study On The Efficacy And Safety of Fexofenadine (Telfast®) 30mg Pediatric Tablets On Filipino Children Aged 6 To 11 for The Relief of Perennial And Intermittent Allergic Rhinitis.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
