  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the safety and efficacy of Fexofenadine (Telfast®) 30mg pediatric tablets on
      Filipino children aged 6 to 11 for the relief of symptoms associated with perennial and
      intermittent allergic rhinitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
